/ End demo
.demo-description
  %h4
    About
  %p
    This jQuery plugin generates
    %a{:href => "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sparkline", :linkindex => "7", :class => :greybox } sparklines
    (small inline charts) directly
    in the browser using data supplied either inline in the HTML, or via javascript.
  %p
    The plugin is compatible with most modern browsers and has been
    tested with Firefox 2+, Safari 3+, Opera 9, Google Chrome and Internet
    Explorer 6, 7 &amp; 8.
  %p
    Each example displayed above takes just 1 line of HTML or javascript to generate.
  %p
    The plugin was written by
